title: 2013 Canary Wharf Squash Classic - Final - Barker vs Willstrop
description:
Grand final match of the 2013 Canary Wharf Squash Classic held at the East Wintergarden of the Canary Wharf Estate, London.  2013 is the 100th running of this classic event that attracts, not only spectators from all over the world, but also the worlds best Squash Players.

Download and enjoy the match, in its entirety, on 720x576@25 video.
